videos.description: The Buffaloes execute a flea flicker perfectly, but Steven Montez's pass to a wide-open Shay Fields falls incomplete off the receiver's hands.
videos.headline: Brutal drop costs Colorado surefire TD

videos.description: Colorado continues to be plagued by drops, as Steven Montez's pass goes through Devin Ross' hands in the end zone.
videos.headline: Buffaloes' Ross can't haul in pass in end zone

videos.description: Phillip Lindsay takes a handoff and cuts into the end zone, scoring from 6 yards out to give the Buffaloes a 10-0 lead.
videos.headline: Lindsay punches it in for Colorado TD

videos.description: Manny Wilkins throws to the right sideline and N'Keal Harry jumps up to reel in the pass for an impressive 22-yard pickup.
videos.headline: Sun Devils WR makes leaping grab along sideline

videos.description: Manny Wilkins escapes pressure in the pocket and takes off, scrambling for a gain of 21 yards and a Sun Devils first down.
videos.headline: Wilkins evades pressure, scrambles for ASU first down

videos.description: Manny Wilkins targets N'Keal Harry in the end zone and Harry contorts his body to make the grab, scoring a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Harry adjusts mid-air to reel in Sun Devils TD

videos.description: Phillip Lindsay gets the ball at the goal line sneaks into the end zone for a 1-yard score, giving Colorado a 17-7 lead.
videos.headline: Buffs' Lindsay pounds it in for second TD of game

videos.description: With under 10 seconds remaining in the first half, Manny Wilkins connects with Kyle Williams for a 25-yard touchdown, cutting Colorado's lead three.
videos.headline: Sun Devils score just before the half with TD

videos.description: Manny Wilkins targets N'Keal Harris and has his pass tipped, but Harris shows his concentration by coming down with the ball for a 17-yard gain.
videos.headline: Harry snares tipped ball for Arizona State first down

videos.description: Steven Montez goes deep, lofting a pass to Shay Fields who takes it to the house for a 54-yard score, giving the Buffaloes a 27-17 lead.
videos.headline: Colorado airs it out for long TD

videos.description: Demario Richard takes a handoff and runs through a Colorado defender to score from 5 yards out and tie the game at 27.
videos.headline: ASU's Richard bowls into end zone to tie game

videos.description: Eno Benjamin breaks several tackles and spins into the end zone for a 19-yard score, giving Arizona State a 34-30 lead.
videos.headline: Sun Devils' RB goes beast mode on go-ahead TD
